{"title":"太阳系的小客人","authors":["高士其"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳系的小客人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高士其"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一颗人造卫星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在苏联上空飞升"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是新的红色的月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕着地球而旋转"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星际旅行不是梦想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不久就要实现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在飞向月宫的路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是第一站"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上的星星都在迎接"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这太阳系的小客人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听！这是天空的音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上的人们正在收听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这音乐发射到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球上每一个角落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它向全世界人民宣告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类一定能征服宇宙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人造卫星是苏联同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对十月革命的献礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是社会主义制度的胜利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是和平力量的胜利"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}